[I] Stringprep, Punycode and IDNA implementation

[T] GNU Libidn is an implementation of the Stringprep, Punycode and IDNA
[T] specifications defined by the IETF Internationalized Domain Names (IDN)
[T] working group, used for internationalized domain names. The package is
[T] available under the GNU Lesser General Public License.

[U] https://www.gnu.org/software/libidn/

